        f"- [x] Start a fresh daily session for existing Task {task_id} work.",
        f"- [x] Reuse the existing Task {task_id} work-tracking folder instead of archiving or recreating it.",
        f"- [x] Repoint `{SESSIONS_CURRENT_REL}` and `{PLANS_CURRENT_REL}` to the active continuation state.",
