        f"- **[{now.strftime('%H:%M')}]** — [S:{session_value}|W:{work_context}|H:scripts/codex-task:sessions-continue|E:{tracker_relative}] Reused the existing Task {task_id} ACTIVE work-tracking folder for a new daily session",
